{"tid":1354660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯天人入黎 一齊抵制元朗","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T07:53:47.000Z","uid":48315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c94a5e7ef7fbe5a39b77a80182cb40fa48b9a030","tid":1354660,"uid":48315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"作為一個天水圍生活左十幾年既人<br />\n相信大家都知道天水圍跟本無咩娛樂 食飯睇戲唱K最近地方就係元朗<br />\n元朗班黑社會跟本直接操控左好多餐廳同鋪頭<br />\n我地係元朗消費跟本就係助長緊呢班垃圾<br />\n<br />\n所以各位屯門 天水圍既巴打<br />\n由今日開始 食飯娛樂都去遠啲 比元朗班仆街知道元朗唔係佢地大撚哂<br />\n如果啲商鋪突然發覺少左好多人幫襯 自然就會制做壓力比班掌權者<br />\n<br />\n希望各位堅持落去!!!!"},{"pid":"1a3c55fad42ade545cc5f5e5bb88adf126fb6b22","tid":1354660,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n做生意靠你班乞衣一百幾十？<br />\n<br />\n人地真正收入都唔知<br />\n<br />\n死返去小學重讀啦"},{"pid":"590f4679b1b03710e17186910347bdf51b10b293","tid":1354660,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3c55fad42ade545cc5f5e5bb88adf126fb6b22","tid":1354660,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n做生意靠你班乞衣一百幾十？<br />\n<br />\n人地真正收入都唔知<br />\n<br />\n死返去小學重讀啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:51:36.000Z","msg":"做過生意未阿柒頭?"},{"pid":"4c9843b568ef9a8916dc5264d35ea2ce42634ced","tid":1354660,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"590f4679b1b03710e17186910347bdf51b10b293","tid":1354660,"uid":243635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3c55fad42ade545cc5f5e5bb88adf126fb6b22","tid":1354660,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n弱智<br />\n<br />\n做生意靠你班乞衣一百幾十？<br />\n<br />\n人地真正收入都唔知<br />\n<br />\n死返去小學重讀啦"}